SwiftGodot/PrimitiveMesh":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PrimitiveMesh"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"PrimitiveMesh","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/PrimitiveMesh","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/primitivemesh","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Base class for all primitive meshes. Handles applying a "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Material","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" to a primitive mesh."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PrimitiveMesh"}]},"doc://SwiftGodot/SH":{"type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/SH","title":"Swift.Hashable"},"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/VariantStorable":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"VariantStorable"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"VariantStorable"}],"title":"VariantStorable","abstract":[{"text":"Types that conform to VariantStorable can be stored in a Variant and can be extracted","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"back out of a Variant.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/VariantStorable","url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/variantstorable"},"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/LightmapGI/directional":{"title":"directional","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"text":", bakes lightmaps to contain directional information as spherical harmonics. This results in more realistic lighting appearance, especially with normal mapped materials and for lights that have their direct light baked (","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Light3D\/lightBakeMode","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" set to "},{"type"